<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Clock-Out Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: #1a1a2e;
      padding: 24px 32px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 4px 0 0 0;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    .body p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #444;
    }
    .detail-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .detail-table td {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .detail-table td:first-child {
      color: #888;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .detail-table td:last-child {
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .detail-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #c0392b;
    }
    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 16px 32px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Clock-Out Reminder</h1>
      <p>{{companyName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi {{employeeName}},</p>
      <p>This is a reminder that your shift is ending soon. Please clock out at your scheduled time.</p>

      <table class="detail-table">
        <tr>
          <td>Clock-In Time</td>
          <td>{{clockInTime}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Scheduled End</td>
          <td class="highlight">{{scheduledEndTime}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p>If you do not clock out, the system will automatically close your session after the grace period has elapsed.</p>

      <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/employee/punch-logs" class="cta">Clock Out</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      This is an automated notification from BizBuddy. Please do not reply to this email.
      &copy; {{currentYear}} BizBuddy LLC.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
